  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      450.65,
      542.78,
      768.82
    ],
    "text": "Very heavy showers about 150mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces. Heavy showers above 100mm are likely at some places in and in Galle and Matara districts. Therefore, general public is advised to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by heavy rain, strong winds and lightning during thundershowers. Situation: Reported rainfall (currently received) from 08.30 a.m. on 14.05.2026 to 08.30 a.m. on 15.05.2026 given below.",
